headline: Match Group to Announce First Quarter 2025 Results
summary: Match Group (NASDAQ: MTCH) will release financial results for the first quarter 2025 on Thursday, May 8, 2025 before market open. The company will host its quarterly conference call to discuss these results at 8:30 a.m. ET on the same day.
